            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide opacity-80">광고 분리</div>
              <p class="mt-1 opacity-95">광고 콘텐츠는 SPONSORED 배지. <a href="/ko/editorial-policy/" class="underline text-white">편집 원칙</a> 공개.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:text-right">
          <a href="/ko/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-white px-6 py-3 text-primary-900" style="font-weight:500; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md)">
            1:1 상담 신청
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          </a>
